*[[Edmund Purdom]] as CEO Steensland
*[[Garrick Hagon]] as Barton (as Garick Hagon)
*[[James Aubrey (actor)|James Aubrey]] as Contek 1
*[[Derrick Vopelka]] as Contek 2
*[[Jed Downey]] as Man on Tapes

==Plot==
An experimental submarine, the "Siren II", with an experienced crew is sent to find out what happened to the "Siren I", mysteriously disappeared in a submarine rift.  Things go awry when they begin to find things that should not be there...

